About Us

Discover Our Passion for Creating Timeless and Innovative Designs

  • History

  • Mission

  • Vision

Founded in 1997, Interioz was born out of a passion for creating beautiful and functional spaces. Over the years, we have grown from a small team of dedicated designers into a leading interior design firm. Our journey began with a simple mission: to transform ordinary spaces into extraordinary experiences. Through innovative design solutions and a commitment to excellence, we have successfully completed numerous projects, each reflecting our dedication to quality and creativity.

At Interioz, our mission is to enhance the lives of our clients by creating spaces that are both aesthetically pleasing and highly functional. We believe that a well-designed environment can significantly impact one's well-being and productivity. Our goal is to deliver personalized design solutions that reflect our clients' unique tastes and needs while maintaining the highest standards of quality and professionalism.

Our vision is to be a global leader in the interior design industry, renowned for our creativity, innovation, and exceptional service. We aspire to continuously push the boundaries of design, embracing new trends and technologies to create spaces that inspire and delight. At Interioz, we are committed to making the world a more beautiful place, one room at a time.

Journey of Interioz

Innovation and Growth

Interioz Founding

Interioz is founded by Alexander Reynolds, with a vision to revolutionize interior design through innovative and sustainable solutions.

1997

First Major Project Completion

Interioz completes its first major commercial project, setting a new standard for contemporary office spaces in the region.

2003 - 2008

Expansion into Residential Design

Expanding its portfolio, Interioz begins taking on residential projects, bringing its unique design philosophy into homes.

2009 - 2014

International Recognition

Interioz gains international recognition, winning several prestigious awards for its innovative and sustainable designs.

2015 - 2019

Opening New Branches

Interioz opens new branches in multiple cities, extending its reach and continuing to set new trends in interior design.

2020 - Present

Discover Our

Our Design Philosophy

At Interioz, we believe that exceptional design should seamlessly blend aesthetics, functionality, and sustainability. Our approach is rooted in a profound understanding of our clients’ needs and the unique context of each project.

We collaborate closely with our clients throughout the entire design process, ensuring that their vision is brought to life in a way that is both beautiful and practical. By integrating environmentally responsible practices, we create spaces that are not only visually stunning but also harmonious with the environment.

Our commitment to excellence drives us to deliver designs that are timeless, innovative, and tailored to enhance the lives of those who inhabit them.

Our Passion for Interior Design

At Interioz, we believe that exceptional interior design goes beyond aesthetics; it’s about creating spaces that inspire, function seamlessly, and respect the environment. Our passion lies in understanding the unique needs and desires of our clients, ensuring that each project reflects their individuality and enhances their daily lives.

We immerse ourselves in the latest design trends and sustainable practices, constantly pushing the boundaries of what’s possible. Our commitment to innovation and excellence allows us to transform ordinary spaces into extraordinary experiences, blending beauty with practicality in every detail.

With a keen eye for detail and a dedication to quality, we strive to create interiors that are not only visually stunning but also harmonious and functional. At Interioz, we are driven by the belief that great design has the power to improve lives, and we are dedicated to making that vision a reality for each of our clients.
